OL,7,FIt's a concern shared by Karen Dry,
OL,8,Fwho now organises vigils for affected
OL,9,Ffamilies in Hull. She says the fight
OL,10,Ffor change will continue in the weeks
OL,11,Fafter the general election on 4 July.
OL,13,F"I now owe it to my parents to make
OL,14,Fsure that this doesn't happen to
OL,15,Fanyone else."
OL,17,F"Whoever takes over (as Prime
OL,18,FMinister) I'm sure will pick up the
OL,19,Fmantle, we'll make sure that they pick
OL,20,Fup the mantle," she said.
