OL,7,F"We're not really going to give them a
OL,8,Fchoice."
OL,10,FFuneral director Kevin Moxon, who runs
OL,11,Fbranches of his business in
OL,12,FScarborough and Hull, says work to
OL,13,Fthat effect is still continuing
OL,14,Fdespite the election.
OL,16,F"Two professional bodies are working
OL,17,Ftogether primarily looking at bringing
OL,18,Ftogether regulations and will be
OL,19,Fadvising whoever takes power," he said.
OL,21,F"That's still taking place."
