OL,12,F"We know that people are incredibly
OL,13,Fvulnerable when they're dealing with
OL,14,Fdeceased loved ones, so there needs to
OL,15,Fbe regulation to protect them," said
OL,16,FEmma Hardy, the Labour MP for Hull
OL,17,FWest and Hessle.
